Sound recorder plug-ins for OpenSesame
Copyright Daniel Schreij (2011-2012)

ABOUT
=====
This is a set of plug-ins for OpenSesame, a graphical experiment builder for the
social sciences. These plug-ins add the ability to record sound from the microphone.

DOCUMENTATION AND INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
===========================================
- <http://osdoc.cogsci.nl/plug-ins/soundrecorder-plug-ins>

DEPENDENCIES
============
- OpenSesame <http://www.cogsci.nl/opensesame>
- PyAudio <http://people.csail.mit.edu/hubert/pyaudio/>